The Climate Investment Program applies the following schemes:
- Scheme for improving the energy efficiency of buildings and other objects (Energy efficiency scheme - CEE);
- Scheme to promote the use of electric vehicles (Scheme electric cars - SEM)

ensure the establishment of small and medium-sized enterprises;
