• remove development barriers related to social instability;
Sustainable just transition in Czech just transition regions

Main objectives of the programme are:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         - to reduce environmental nuisances to the maximum extent possible in order to protect the environment, human health, well-being, property and cultural heritage;
- to promote sustainable development in order to secure an environment that meets the human health and well-being needs of the present generation and future generations;
- to preserve and protecti natural diversity;
- the good state of the environment;
- the prevention of damage to the environment and the remedying of damage caused to the environment.
